<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>목사고시 기출문제(2015-2025)</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --ink: #1c1a17;
    --paper: #f4efe6;
    --paper-2: #ece4d6;
    --card: #fbf8f1;
    --line: #d8cdb9;
    --burgundy: #7a2230;
    --burgundy-soft: #9c3a48;
    --gold: #b08545;
    --green: #3f6b48;
    --green-soft: #e3efe3;
    --red: #a23030;
    --red-soft: #f6e3e0;
    --muted: #7c7363;
    --shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(40,30,15,.06), 0 8px 24px rgba(40,30,15,.07);
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body {
    font-family: "Apple SD Gothic Neo", "Malgun Gothic", "Noto Sans KR", sans-serif;
    background: var(--paper); color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.65;
  }
  .app-container { max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px 20px 80px; }
  header { border-bottom: 2px solid var(--ink); padding-bottom: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px 16px; }
  .title-block { min-width: 0; }
  h1 { font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--burgundy); white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.15; }
  .subtitle { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 3px; letter-spacing: 0.03em; }
  .header-actions { display: flex; align-items: flex-end; gap: 14px; font-size: 0.78rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-left: auto; }
  .hdr-link { background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: underline; white-space: nowrap; padding: 2px 0; color: var(--ink); font-size: 0.78rem; }
  .hdr-link.gold { color: var(--gold); }
  .hdr-link.red { color: var(--red); }

  .dashboard { display: flex; gap: 5px; margin-bottom: 15px; background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px; box-shadow: var(--shadow); }
  .dash-item { flex: 1; text-align: center; border-right: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .dash-item:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .dash-title { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--muted); }
  .dash-score { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: bold; color: var(--burgundy); }
  .dash-sub { font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--muted); }

  .filters-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .filters { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; align-items: center; }
  .chip {
    padding: 6px 12px; background: var(--paper-2); border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--muted); cursor: pointer; transition: 0.2s;
  }
  .chip.on { background: var(--burgundy); color: #fff; border-color: var(--burgundy); }
  .chip.pick.on::before { content: "✓ "; }

  .adv-wrap { position: relative; }
  .adv-toggle { background: var(--paper-2); border: 1px dashed var(--line); color: var(--muted); }
  #adv-panel {
    display: none; position: absolute; right: 0; top: 42px; z-index: 10;
    background: var(--paper-2); padding: 12px; border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid var(--line);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow); min-width: 240px; gap: 10px; flex-direction: column;
  }
  #adv-panel.show { display: flex; }
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    #adv-panel { left: 0; right: 0; width: 100%; }
  }

  #search-box { width: 100%; padding: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 8px; font-size: 0.95rem; }

  .mode-tabs { display: flex; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .mode-tab { flex: 1; padding: 12px; text-align: center; background: var(--paper-2); cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; border: none; color: var(--muted); }
  .mode-tab.on { background: var(--ink); color: #fff; }

  .card { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; box-shadow: var(--shadow); margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .q-meta { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--gold); font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 8px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
  .meta-right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
  .meta-link { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--muted); text-decoration: underline; cursor: pointer; }
  .star { cursor: pointer; }
  .q-text { font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px; word-break: keep-all; }
  .opt {
    display: block; width: 100%; text-align: left; padding: 14px 16px; margin-bottom: 8px;
    background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 1rem;
  }
  .opt.selected { background: var(--burgundy-soft); color: white; border-color: var(--burgundy); }
  .opt.correct { background: var(--green-soft); border-color: var(--green); color: var(--green); font-weight: bold; }
  .opt.wrong { background: var(--red-soft); border-color: var(--red); color: var(--red); text-decoration: line-through; }

  /* 보기 소거 */
  .opt-row { display: flex; align-items: stretch; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .opt-row .opt { margin-bottom: 0; flex: 1; }
  .opt-x {
    flex-shrink: 0; width: 44px; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 8px;
    background: #fff; color: var(--muted); font-size: 1rem; cursor: pointer; line-height: 1;
  }
  .opt-x:active { transform: translateY(1px); }
  .opt-x.on { background: var(--ink); color: #fff; border-color: var(--ink); }
  .opt.eliminated { opacity: .4; text-decoration: line-through; background: var(--paper-2); color: var(--muted); }

  /* 유틸리티 바: 글자 크기 + 백업 표시 */
  .util-bar { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 10px; margin: 4px 0 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .font-ctrl { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
  .font-lbl { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--muted); }
  .font-btn { padding: 3px 10px; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 6px; background: #fff; color: var(--ink); font-size: 0.8rem; cursor: pointer; }
  .font-btn:active { transform: translateY(1px); }
  .backup-note { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--muted); }
  .backup-note.warn { color: var(--red); }

  /* 글자 크기 스케일: 문제·보기·해설에 적용 */
  .q-text { font-size: calc(1.15rem * var(--fscale, 1)); }
  .opt { font-size: calc(1rem * var(--fscale, 1)); }
  .fb-exp { font-size: calc(0.88rem * var(--fscale, 1)); }

  /* 오답노트 리스트 뷰 */
  .rv-head { font-weight: bold; color: var(--burgundy); margin: 4px 2px 12px; font-size: 1.05rem; }
  .rv-card { padding: 16px; }
  .rv-meta { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .rv-tag { background: var(--paper-2); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1px 8px; color: var(--ink); }
  .rv-ok  { color: var(--green); font-weight: bold; }
  .rv-bad { color: var(--red);   font-weight: bold; }
  .rv-q { font-size: calc(1.02rem * var(--fscale, 1)); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; word-break: keep-all; }
  .rv-opts { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .rv-opt { font-size: calc(0.92rem * var(--fscale, 1)); padding: 8px 10px; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 6px; color: var(--muted); }
  .rv-opt.correct { background: var(--green-soft); border-color: var(--green); color: var(--green); font-weight: bold; }
  .rv-exp { font-size: calc(0.85rem * var(--fscale, 1)); line-height: 1.6; background: var(--paper-2); border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 12px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: var(--ink); }
  .rv-go { width: 100%; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid var(--burgundy); border-radius: 8px; background: #fff; color: var(--burgundy); font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.85rem; cursor: pointer; }
  .rv-go:active { transform: translateY(1px); }

  /* 문제 번호 점프 */
  .q-counter { cursor: pointer; text-decoration: underline dotted; text-underline-offset: 3px; }
  .jump-wrap { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
  .jump-input { width: 64px; padding: 4px 6px; border: 1px solid var(--burgundy); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.9rem; text-align: center; }
  .jump-btn { padding: 4px 10px; border: none; border-radius: 6px; background: var(--burgundy); color: #fff; font-size: 0.85rem; cursor: pointer; }
  .jump-btn.ghost { background: #fff; color: var(--muted); border: 1px solid var(--line); }

  .ans-box { margin: 10px 0 12px; padding: 14px; background: var(--paper-2); border-left: 4px solid var(--gold); display: none; border-radius: 8px; }

  /* 듀오링고식 피드백 패널 (보기 바로 아래, 인라인) */
  .fb-panel { margin-top: 14px; padding: 16px; border-radius: 12px; animation: fbPop .18s ease; }
  @keyframes fbPop { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(6px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
  .fb-panel.ok  { background: var(--green-soft); border: 1px solid var(--green); }
  .fb-panel.bad { background: var(--red-soft);   border: 1px solid var(--red); }
  .fb-head { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 9px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .fb-icon { width: 26px; height: 26px; border-radius: 50%; color: #fff; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .fb-panel.ok  .fb-icon { background: var(--green); }
  .fb-panel.bad .fb-icon { background: var(--red); }
  .fb-title { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; }
  .fb-panel.ok  .fb-title { color: var(--green); }
  .fb-panel.bad .fb-title { color: var(--red); }
  .fb-exp { font-size: 0.88rem; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 12px; color: var(--ink);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.72); border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 12px; }
  .fb-exp:empty { display: none; }
  .fb-tags { display: flex; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .fb-tag { font-size: 0.78rem; padding: 6px 13px; background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 20px; color: var(--red); cursor: pointer; }
  .fb-tag:active { transform: translateY(1px); }
  .fb-gemini { width: 100%; padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #5b6ee0; border-radius: 10px; background: #eef0ff; color: #3b46b0; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.9rem; cursor: pointer; margin-bottom: 9px; }
  .fb-gemini:active { transform: translateY(1px); }
  .fb-next { width: 100%; padding: 15px; border: none; border-radius: 12px; color: #fff; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.95rem; cursor: pointer; transition: transform .05s, box-shadow .05s; }
  .fb-panel.ok  .fb-next { background: var(--green); box-shadow: 0 4px 0 #2c4d33; }
  .fb-panel.bad .fb-next { background: var(--red);   box-shadow: 0 4px 0 #7a1d1d; }
  .fb-next:active { transform: translateY(3px); box-shadow: none; }
  .opt.answered { pointer-events: none; }
  .tag-wrap { display: none; margin-top: 12px; padding-top: 10px; border-top: 1px dashed var(--line); }
  .tag-title { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .tag-area { display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .tag-btn { padding: 8px 12px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--line); cursor: pointer; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; }
  .tag-btn.t1 { background: #fff3c4; border-color: #e2c36a; }
  .tag-btn.t2 { background: #dff0ff; border-color: #7ab4e4; }
  .tag-btn.t3 { background: #ffe0e0; border-color: #e38b8b; }

  .nav-btns { display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 15px; }
  .nav-btn { flex: 1; padding: 14px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; border: 1px solid var(--line); background: var(--card); }
  .nav-btn.primary { background: var(--ink); color: #fff; }

  .exam-timer { background: var(--burgundy); color: white; padding: 10px; text-align: center; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 8px; }
  .no-timer { background: var(--paper-2); color: var(--muted); border: 1px dashed var(--line); }
  #toast { visibility: hidden; position: fixed; top: 12px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); background: var(--burgundy); color: white; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 30px; z-index: 1000; pointer-events: none; white-space: nowrap; }
  #toast.show { visibility: visible; animation: fadeInOut 1.8s; }
  #toast.ok  { background: var(--green); }   /* 정답 - 초록 */
  #toast.bad { background: var(--red); }      /* 오답 - 빨강 */
  @keyframes fadeInOut { 0%, 100% { opacity: 0; } 15%, 85% { opacity: 1; } }

  /* 업데이트 내역 */
  .ver-btn { background:none; border:none; cursor:pointer; color:var(--muted); text-decoration:underline; position:relative; font-size:0.75rem; white-space:nowrap; }
  .ver-dot { position:absolute; top:-3px; right:-7px; width:7px; height:7px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--red); display:none; }
  .ver-dot.show { display:block; }
  .cl-overlay { display:none; position:fixed; inset:0; background:rgba(20,15,8,.45); z-index:2000; align-items:center; justify-content:center; padding:18px; }
  .cl-overlay.show { display:flex; }
  .cl-box { background:var(--card); border-radius:14px; max-width:430px; width:100%; max-height:80vh; overflow:auto; box-shadow:var(--shadow); }
  .cl-head { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; padding:15px 18px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); font-weight:bold; color:var(--burgundy); position:sticky; top:0; background:var(--card); }
  .cl-head button { background:none; border:none; font-size:1.1rem; cursor:pointer; color:var(--muted); line-height:1; }
  .cl-entry { padding:14px 18px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); }
  .cl-entry:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
  .cl-ver { font-weight:bold; color:var(--burgundy); font-size:0.95rem; margin-bottom:7px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; }
  .cl-date { font-size:0.72rem; color:var(--muted); font-weight:normal; }
  .cl-new { font-size:0.68rem; background:var(--red); color:#fff; border-radius:10px; padding:1px 7px; font-weight:bold; }
  .cl-entry.seen { opacity:.55; }
  .cl-entry.seen .cl-ver { color:var(--muted); }
  .cl-note { font-size:0.9rem; margin:3px 0; padding-left:13px; position:relative; }
  .cl-note::before { content:"·"; position:absolute; left:3px; }

  /* 초기화 선택 모달 */
  .reset-opt { width:100%; text-align:left; padding:14px; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:10px; background:#fff; cursor:pointer; }
  .reset-opt:active { transform:translateY(1px); }
  .reset-opt.danger { border-color:var(--red); }
  .reset-opt-t { font-weight:bold; font-size:0.98rem; margin-bottom:4px; color:var(--ink); }
  .reset-opt.danger .reset-opt-t { color:var(--red); }
  .reset-opt-d { font-size:0.8rem; color:var(--muted); line-height:1.5; }
  .cl-banner { display:none; background:var(--burgundy); color:#fff; padding:10px 14px; border-radius:8px; margin-bottom:14px; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:10px; font-size:0.9rem; }
  .cl-banner.show { display:flex; }
  .cl-banner .cl-see { background:#fff; color:var(--burgundy); border:none; border-radius:6px; padding:5px 11px; font-weight:bold; cursor:pointer; font-size:0.83rem; white-space:nowrap; }
  .cl-banner .cl-x { background:none; border:none; color:#fff; font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; padding:0 2px; line-height:1; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="app-container">
  <header>
    <div class="title-block">
      <h1>목사고시 기출문제</h1>
      <div class="subtitle">2015–2025</div>
    </div>
    <div class="header-actions">
      <button class="ver-btn" id="ver-btn" onclick="openChangelog()"><span id="ver-label">v15(260623)</span><span class="ver-dot" id="ver-dot"></span></button>
      <button class="hdr-link gold" onclick="refreshApp()">새로고침</button>
      <button class="hdr-link" onclick="backupProgress()">백업</button>
      <button class="hdr-link" onclick="restoreProgress()">복원</button>
      <button class="hdr-link red" onclick="openResetMenu()">초기화</button>
      <input type="file" id="restore-file" style="display:none;" onchange="handleRestore(event)">
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="util-bar">
    <div class="font-ctrl">
      <span class="font-lbl">글자</span>
      <button class="font-btn" onclick="adjustFont(-1)">가-</button>
      <button class="font-btn" onclick="adjustFont(1)">가+</button>
    </div>
    <div class="backup-note" id="backup-note"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="cl-banner" id="cl-banner">
    <span>✨ 업데이트되었습니다!</span>
    <span style="display:flex; gap:6px; align-items:center;">
      <button class="cl-see" onclick="openChangelog()">변경사항 보기</button>
      <button class="cl-x" onclick="dismissBanner()">✕</button>
    </span>
  </div>

  <div class="dashboard">
    <div class="dash-item"><div class="dash-title">성경 정답률</div><div class="dash-score" id="score-bible">0%</div></div>
    <div class="dash-item"><div class="dash-title">교회사 정답률</div><div class="dash-score" id="score-history">0%</div></div>
    <div class="dash-item"><div class="dash-title">헌법 정답률</div><div class="dash-score" id="score-law">0%</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="dashboard">
    <div class="dash-item"><div class="dash-title">연속 학습일</div><div class="dash-score" id="stat-streak">0일</div></div>
    <div class="dash-item"><div class="dash-title">전체 진도</div><div class="dash-score" id="stat-progress">0%</div></div>
    <div class="dash-item"><div class="dash-title">오늘 복습</div><div class="dash-score" id="stat-due">0</div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="filters-group">
    <div class="filters" id="year-chips"></div>
    <div class="filters">
      <button class="chip subj-f on" data-subj="all">전체 과목</button>
      <button class="chip subj-f" data-subj="성경">성경</button>
      <button class="chip subj-f" data-subj="교회사">교회사</button>
      <button class="chip subj-f" data-subj="헌법">헌법</button>
      <button class="chip" data-filter="shuffle">🔀 랜덤 섞기</button>
    </div>
    <input id="search-box" type="text" placeholder="🔍 문제 키워드 검색...">
    <div class="filters">
      <button class="chip" data-filter="due">📅 오늘 복습</button>
      <button class="chip" data-filter="wrong">❌ 오답만</button>
      <button class="chip" data-filter="bookmark">⭐ 별표</button>
      <div class="adv-wrap">
        <button class="chip adv-toggle" onclick="toggleAdv(event)">⚙️ 고급</button>
        <div id="adv-panel">
          <div class="filters">
            <button class="chip" data-filter="weak">🎯 약점 집중(상위20%)</button>
          </div>
          <select id="tag-filter" style="padding:8px; border-radius:6px; border:1px solid var(--line);">
            <option value="all">🏷 모든 오답 태그</option>
            <option value="헷갈림">헷갈림</option>
            <option value="암기부족">암기부족</option>
            <option value="실수">실수</option>
          </select>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mode-tabs">
    <button class="mode-tab on" data-mode="study">학습</button>
    <button class="mode-tab" data-mode="yearly">기출</button>
    <button class="mode-tab" style="color:var(--red);" data-mode="exam">모의</button>
    <button class="mode-tab" data-mode="review">오답노트</button>
  </div>

  <div id="content-area"></div>
</div>
<div id="toast"></div>

<div class="cl-overlay" id="changelog-modal" onclick="closeChangelogBg(event)">
  <div class="cl-box">
    <div class="cl-head"><span>📋 업데이트 내역</span><button onclick="closeChangelog()" aria-label="닫기">✕</button></div>
    <div id="cl-body"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="cl-overlay" id="reset-modal" onclick="closeResetBg(event)">
  <div class="cl-box" style="max-width:360px;">
    <div class="cl-head"><span>초기화</span><button onclick="closeResetMenu()" aria-label="닫기">✕</button></div>
    <div style="padding:16px 18px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:12px;">
      <button class="reset-opt" onclick="resetScores()">
        <div class="reset-opt-t">점수만 초기화</div>
        <div class="reset-opt-d">정답률·진도·통계·복습 일정을 0으로. 오답노트와 별표는 그대로 둡니다. (정답률 다시 도전용)</div>
      </button>
      <button class="reset-opt danger" onclick="resetAll()">
        <div class="reset-opt-t">전체 초기화</div>
        <div class="reset-opt-d">오답노트·별표까지 모든 기록을 삭제합니다. 되돌릴 수 없어요.</div>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
